#

Warm Vegetable Salad with Roasted Garlic Vinaigrette

$15
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Tags:

VegetableSaladWarmHealthyVegan

Description

A vibrant mix of seasonal vegetables, roasted to perfection and drizzled with a flavorful garlic vinaigrette.

Ingredients

  • Zucchini: 2 medium, sliced
  • Bell Peppers: 1 red, 1 yellow, diced
  • Carrots: 2 large, peeled and sliced
  • Cherry Tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • Red Onion: 1 medium, sliced
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Fresh Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Balsamic Vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Fresh Basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Feta Cheese (optional): 1/2 cup, crumbled
